metadata.name: Distance Reiki with Judith
metadata.description: A distance Kundalini Reiki session (1-1.5 hours). There is much more in this world than what we as humans can perceive through our five senses. I tap in to your energetic body. On that level there is an enormous amount of information about who you are stored. For example: physical pain is often caused by repressed emotions. When I enter this deeper level, it becomes possible to heal the issue from its roots. That is why a treatment has huge healing possibilities. Energy is not bound by place and time; it is therefore possible to receive distance treatments from anywhere in the world. More information on www.yugenwithjudith.com.
